				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1874e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Except as provided in paragraph (b) of this section, insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1051470.dita#i1051470"
                        base="i1051470"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.229-3</xref>, Federal, State, and Local Taxes, in solicitations and contracts if-</p>
					          <ol id="d1860e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1874e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contract is to be performed wholly or partly in the United States or its outlying areas;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1874e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A fixed-price contract is contemplated; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1874e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contract is expected to exceed the simplified acquisition threshold.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1874e59" class="- topic/p ">
